                           <p>Brief fragment recounting the violent overthrow of the Timurid or Mughal Emperor <persName key="viaf_70169499" role="subject">Shāh ʿĀlam</persName> and the temporary installation of <persName key="person_f7111" role="subject">Prince Bīdārbakht</persName> as <persName key="person_f7111" role="subject">Emperor Jahān Shāh II</persName> by the rebel <persName key="person_f7138" role="subject">Ghulām Qādir Khān</persName>, in opposition to <persName key="person_f7251" role="object">Mahādjī Sindhiyah</persName> and the <orgName>Maratha confederacy</orgName>, in 1790
